textBeforeTable: The Discraft Elite Z Dyed XL is an extra long range driver with stability ratings of 0.0 to 1.5 (stable to moderately overstable). The Pro-D XL is a terrific beginner friendly golf disc that files straight with very little fade. It is easy to control and holds an almost perfect line on big throws. Good for rollers, turnover forehand/backhand shots, and as a flick roller. It is the former world distance record holder at 693 feet. Popular with players of all skill levels.
